      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i was looking at some flight tracker maps earlier and noticed something weird. it seems like there are way more flights circling or crossing over certain cities like london or nyc at really specific intervals thats not just normal traffic patterns... like they seem to be tracing specific shapes or lines if u look at the density. can u help me look into why those specific paths are so repetitive? i feel like there is a method to it",
